# AI Instructions

When generating simulation systems:

- Design for autonomous worlds.
- Support headless execution.
- Collect meaningful metrics.
- Detect failures automatically.
- Simulate long periods efficiently.
- Never depend on rendering.
- Prioritize reproducibility.
- Produce human-readable reports.